Example names for KPI's:
Potentially break down the KPI's to two sections:
Business KPI's that includes:
Trustpilot reviews
Visitor satisfaction rate
the number of educational programs offered
Percentage of repeat visitors
revenue growth rate

Website KPI's that includes:
Page load time(Length the page loads)
Bounce rate(The amount of users that visit a website then leaves immediately)
Traffic by sources(Allows developers to see what devices are used by users)
Conversion rate(How well the user and customers to complete a desired task)
Average time on page(The average time user spends on the page)

